<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>AI 이미지 생성기 - 홈</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif; text-align: center; padding: 100px; background-color: #f8f9fa; }
        .container { background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); display: inline-block; }
        h1 { color: #333; }
        input { padding: 15px; width: 400px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 16px; }
        button { padding: 15px 30px; background-color: #007bff; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 16px; margin-left: 10px; }
        button:hover { background-color: #0056b3; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>🎨 AI Image Generator</h1>
    <p>상상하는 이미지를 텍스트로 입력해보세요.</p>
    <form action="/generate" method="GET">
        <input type="text" name="prompt" placeholder="예: 우주에서 서핑하는 고양이" required>
        <button type="submit">생성하기</button>
    </form>
</div>
</body>
</html>